featured_reviews.review_id:
The beautiful masjid in Kohima town. The largest masjid in the town area. I lived here for a long time. I love this masjid. And I miss also. The most essential masjid for this town area................
It's system is so good and it has a clean management. Almost a holy place in this town. So we should attend here every five-time jamat and should try to increase the attendance of ummah.

Near naga bazar area, Kohima, Nagalang - 797001.
